#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.175"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.175:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.175:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: upāsakacaṇḍālasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.175:0.3"
msgid "175. Caṇḍālasutta"
msgstr "175. Outcaste"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: upāsakapatikuṭṭho ca → upāsakapatikiṭṭho ca (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.175:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako upāsakacaṇḍālo ca hoti "
"upāsakamalañca upāsakapatikuṭṭho ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a lay follower with five qualities is an outcaste, a stain, and "
"a reject among lay followers."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.175:1.3"
msgid "Assaddho hoti;"
msgstr "They’re faithless."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.4"
msgid "dussīlo hoti;"
msgstr "They’re unethical."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.5"
msgid "kotūhalamaṅgaliko hoti, maṅgalaṃ pacceti no kammaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"They practice noisy, superstitious rites, believing in omens rather than "
"deeds."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.6"
msgid "ito ca bahiddhā dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati;"
msgstr ""
"They seek outside of the Buddhist community for teachers worthy of offerings."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.7"
msgid "tattha ca pubbakāraṃ karoti."
msgstr "And they make offerings there first."

msgctxt "an5.175:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako upāsakacaṇḍālo ca "
"hoti upāsakamalañca upāsakapatikuṭṭho ca."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower with these five qualities is an outcaste, a stain, and a "
"reject among lay followers."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: upāsakapuṇḍarīkañca → upāsakapuṇḍarīko ca (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.175:2.1"
msgid ""
"Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako upāsakaratanañca hoti "
"upāsakapadumañca upāsakapuṇḍarīkañca."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower with five qualities is a gem, a pink lotus, and a white lotus "
"among lay followers."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.175:2.3"
msgid "Saddho hoti;"
msgstr "They’re faithful."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.4"
msgid "sīlavā hoti;"
msgstr "They’re ethical."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.5"
msgid "akotūhalamaṅgaliko hoti, kammaṃ pacceti no maṅgalaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"They don’t practice noisy, superstitious rites, and believe in deeds rather "
"than omens."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.6"
msgid "na ito bahiddhā dakkhiṇeyyaṃ gavesati;"
msgstr ""
"They don’t seek outside of the Buddhist community for teachers worthy of "
"offerings."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.7"
msgid "idha ca pubbakāraṃ karoti."
msgstr "And they don’t make offerings there first."

msgctxt "an5.175:2.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako upāsakaratanañca "
"hoti upāsakapadumañca upāsakapuṇḍarīkañcā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A lay follower with these five qualities is a gem, a pink lotus, and a white "
"lotus among lay followers.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.175:2.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
